# Trademark

The code in this repository is open source under the MIT License (see LICENSE).
The name "Lembic" and the Lembic logo are not.

You are free to use, modify, and redistribute the code under the MIT terms. If
you ship a fork or a derivative, please give it your own name, and do not use
the Lembic name or logo in a way that suggests your version is the official
project or is endorsed by it.

This is a lightweight notice, not a registered trademark. The goal is narrow:
keep the name pointing at one project, so people can tell what is official and
what is a fork.
